org.gvsig.fmap.dal.feature.rule

Interface CheckMandatoryAttributesRule

  • All Superinterfaces:
    FeatureRule

    public interface CheckMandatoryAttributesRule
extends FeatureRule
    Empty interface to tag the FeatureRule that check the compliance of mandatory attributes. This is used to check if there is already a rule that checks this in a certain feature type.
